high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the knife to the right of the tomato on the counter.
Cut up the potato to the right of the tomato on the counter.
Take a step back and look at the cabinets below the sink.
Place the knife in the left cabinet below the sink and then close the cabinet.
Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up a piece of the cut up potato.
Walk to the microwave above the dishwasher.
Microwave the piece of potato and then pick up the piece of potato from the microwave.
Turn around and walk  to the green trash can next to the stove.
Place the piece of potato into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of potato into the green trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter between the tomato and the potato.
Slice the potato on the counter into rings.
Turn and face the sink to the left.
Put the knife inside the cupboard under the sink.
Turn right and look up at the counter.
Take a potato slice from the counter.
Turn right and face the microwave on your left.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave and remove the potato slice.
Turn left then right and walk to the green trash can next to the stove.
Put the potato slice in the green trash can.
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato slice in the microwave, throw the potato slice into the trash.

high_descs: Move to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the butter knife that's on the counter to the right of the sink.
Slice the brown roll on the counter using the knife.
Back up a step and center yourself with the sink while carrying the butter knife.
Open the cupboard beneath the left side of the sink, and place the butter knife inside.
Move back to stand close to the counter where you previously sliced the roll.
Pick up a slice of the roll from the counter.
Turn and move to stand in front of the microwave while holding the roll.
Place the roll inside the microwave, turn it on, and then remove it once warmed.
Carry the slice of roll to the trash bin, which is in the corner to the left of the stove.
Place the slice of roll in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a slice of warmed roll.
